OL,3,CTrio guilty of displaying images of
OL,4,Cparagliders at pro-Palestinian march
OL,6,FThree women who displayed images of
OL,7,F"paragliders" at a pro-Palestinian
OL,8,Fmarch in central London a week after
OL,9,FHamas militants entered Israel have
OL,10,Fbeen found guilty of a terror offence.
OL,12,FHeba Alhayek, 29, and Pauline Ankunda,
OL,13,F26, attached images to their backs
OL,14,Fwith tape, while Noimutu Olayinka
OL,15,FTaiwo, 27, stuck one to the handle of
OL,16,Fa placard.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]
