OL,3,CTrio guilty of displaying images of
OL,4,Cparagliders at pro-Palestinian march
OL,6,FBut the trio, who lowered their heads
OL,7,Fand wept in the dock as the verdict
OL,8,Fwas read out, were spared jail after
OL,9,Fthe judge decided their lesson had
OL,10,Fbeen "well learned".
OL,12,FThe women displayed the images on
OL,13,FOctober 14 2023, just seven days after
OL,14,Fmilitants from Hamas launched a
OL,15,Fsurprise aerial assault to enter
OL,16,FIsrael from Gaza on October 7 before
OL,17,Fkilling more than 1,000 Israelis.
