OL,4,Cparagliders at pro-Palestinian march
OL,6,FLawyers for the group had suggested
OL,7,Fthey were actually displaying images
OL,8,Fof a parachute emoji rather than
OL,9,Fparagliders, and that flying-related
OL,10,Fimages were a common symbol of peace
OL,11,Fin the region.
OL,13,FMark Summers KC, for Alhayek and
OL,14,FAnkunda, claimed the idea that the
OL,15,Fimage represented a paraglider started
OL,16,Fwith "an internet group with an
OL,17,Fagenda".
