OL,6,FGiving his verdict, Deputy Senior
OL,7,FDistrict Judge Tan Ikram agreed that
OL,8,Fthe image had been "wrongly described"
OL,9,Fas a paraglider by the police and
OL,10,Fprosecution.
OL,12,FHe added that there was no evidence
OL,13,Fthat any of women supported Hamas, but
OL,14,Fsaid it "matters not" because the
OL,15,Fissue came down to what a "reasonable
OL,16,Fperson" would think the picture meant.
