OL,6,FSection 13 of the Terrorism Act is a
OL,7,Fstrict liability offence, meaning the
OL,8,Fmotivation of the trio was not a
OL,9,Ffactor in the case, but the
OL,10,Finterpretation of a "reasonable
OL,11,Fperson" was.
OL,13,FMr Ikram said "a reasonable person
OL,14,Fwould have seen and read" about Hamas
OL,15,Fmilitants' use of "what was described
OL,16,Fby the media as paragliders", and
OL,17,Fwould therefore associate the image
OL,18,Fwith that tactic.
