OL,3,CTrio guilty of displaying images of
OL,4,Cparagliders at pro-Palestinian march
OL,6,FLawyers for the group argued that
OL,7,Fflying-related images were a common
OL,8,Fsymbol of peace in the region, but the
OL,9,Fjudge said he did not believe a
OL,10,Freasonable person would interpret the
OL,11,Fimage "merely as a symbol of freedom."
OL,13,FMr Ikram said he had "decided not to
OL,14,Fpunish" the defendants, and handed
OL,15,Feach woman a 12-month conditional
OL,16,Fdischarge, meaning they will not face
OL,17,Fpunishment unless they commit further
OL,18,Foffences.
