OL,6,F"You crossed the line, but it would
OL,7,Fhave been fair to say that emotions
OL,8,Fran very high on this issue," he added.
OL,10,F"Your lesson has been well learned.
OL,12,F"I do not find you were seeking to
OL,13,Fshow any support for Hamas."
OL,15,FAlhayek and Ankunda were each ordered
OL,16,Fto pay costs of #400, while no such
OL,17,Forder was made for Taiwo.
OL,19,FThey must pay a surcharge of #26.
