OL,6,FAfter the Metropolitan Police launched
OL,7,Fa social media appeal to find them,
OL,8,FAlhayek and Ankunda handed themselves
OL,9,Fin to Croydon Police Station.
OL,11,FIn a police interview, the pair
OL,12,Finitially claimed someone at the
OL,13,Fdemonstration "who was not known to
OL,14,Fthem" had stuck the images to their
OL,15,Fbacks, before changing their
OL,16,Fstatements, admitting they had
OL,17,Fattached them themselves.
OL,19,F"Their reaction was firstly to lie,"
OL,20,Fprosecutor Brett Weaver told the court.
