OL,6,FNick Price, head of the CPS Special
OL,7,FCrime and Counter Terrorism Division,
OL,8,Fsaid: "All three women knowingly
OL,9,Fdisplayed the images of paragliders in
OL,10,Fcentral London and therefore showed
OL,11,Ftheir support for Hamas, a proscribed
OL,12,Fterrorist organisation.
OL,14,F"The fact that these images were being
OL,15,Fdisplayed in the context of a protest
OL,16,Fopposing the Israeli response to the
OL,17,FHamas attacks demonstrates a
OL,18,Fglorification of the actions taken by
OL,19,Fthe group.
