OL,10,Fof encouraging others to support Hamas.
OL,12,F"When people break the law, whether by
OL,13,Fhateful speech, supporting proscribed
OL,14,Forganisations or by threatening public
OL,15,Forder, we prosecute swiftly and
OL,16,Findependently.
